This paper deals with medical image processing tasks such as segmentation, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of a new attention module for neural networks, which is a topic of interest in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the efficiency and scalability of the proposed method, which is relevant to the fields of neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM).
